      <title>法国智利男子因谋杀日本前女友被判28年监禁 - 报道</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/french-chilean-man-sentenced-28-years-prison-murdering-japanese-ex-girlfriend-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据法新社周四报道，法国上诉法院周四确认一名智利男子犯有 2016 年谋杀日本前女友的罪行，并维持 28 年监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/french-chilean-man-sentenced-28-years-prison-murdering-japanese-ex-girlfriend-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 15:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>团结一致的中国回族哀悼在地震中丧生的女孩</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/tight-knit-chinese-hui-ethnic-minority-mourns-loss-girl-quake-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，中国西北地震灾区杨洼村的回族社区正在哀悼八岁的马金媛，她在家中睡觉时，墙体倒塌，她在墙体废墟下丧生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/tight-knit-chinese-hui-ethnic-minority-mourns-loss-girl-quake-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 14:49:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥总统周四将与拜登通话，关注移民问题</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/mexican-president-speak-biden-thursday-migration-eyed-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩兹·奥夫拉多尔表示，他将于周四上午与美国总统乔·拜登通话，两人可能讨论移民问题，因为人们担心过境点增加和贸易中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/mexican-president-speak-biden-thursday-migration-eyed-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 14:37:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰希望本周找到解除与波兰边境封锁的方法</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-hopes-find-ways-unblock-border-with-poland-this-week-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰副总理周四表示，乌克兰希望本周与波兰新政府达成协议，结束两国边境口岸的卡车封锁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-hopes-find-ways-unblock-border-with-poland-this-week-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 13:58:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京的潜在挑战者否认与前石油老板霍多尔科夫斯基有联系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putins-would-be-challenger-denies-link-former-oil-boss-khodorkovsky-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[寻求在俄罗斯下一届总统选举中与弗拉基米尔·普京竞争的叶卡捷琳娜·邓佐娃周四否认自己得到了一位前石油老板的支持，这位前石油老板在国外经营反对派运动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/putins-would-be-challenger-denies-link-former-oil-boss-khodorkovsky-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 13:52:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中美高级军事官员一年多来首次讲话</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-top-military-officials-spoke-thursday-pentagon-statement-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼表示，美国最高军官周四与中国国防部长举行了一次虚拟会议，这是一年多来的首次此类对话，美国官员希望这可能会导致两国军队之间关系的更广泛恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-china-top-military-officials-spoke-thursday-pentagon-statement-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 13:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>干燥的加沙居民称赞来自埃及的水“像糖”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/parched-gaza-residents-praise-water-tasting-like-sugar-egypt-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于加沙居民扎基·阿布·斯莱马来说，以色列数周的轰炸和围困让他和其他许多人喝着不干净的咸水，现在从埃及海水淡化项目流入这片被毁的飞地的水尝起来“像糖”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/parched-gaza-residents-praise-water-tasting-like-sugar-egypt-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 13:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西警方对布拉斯科姆地面严重破坏发起突击搜查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazil-police-launch-raids-over-braskems-sinking-ground-havoc-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西联邦警察周四进行了突击搜查，调查石化生产商 Braskem 在马塞约市发生的地下严重破坏事件，自 2018 年以来，该事件已迫使约 6 万人搬迁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazil-police-launch-raids-over-braskems-sinking-ground-havoc-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 13:38:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基辅称，俄罗斯迄今已在战争中发射了 7,400 枚导弹和 3,700 架 Shahed 无人机</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-has-fired-7400-missiles-3700-shahed-drones-war-so-far-kyiv-says-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基辅周四表示，俄罗斯在长达 22 个月的入侵过程中向乌克兰目标发射了约 7,400 枚导弹和 3,700 架“沙希德”攻击无人机，这表明莫斯科空中袭击的规模之大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-has-fired-7400-missiles-3700-shahed-drones-war-so-far-kyiv-says-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 13:10:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利总理欧尔班批评乌克兰在边境阻止前总统的举动</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hungarys-pm-orban-criticises-ukraines-move-stop-ex-president-border-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维克托·欧尔班在周四的新闻发布会上表示，乌克兰决定阻止前总统波罗申科本月早些时候离开该国会见匈牙利总理，这引发了人们对基辅欧盟雄心的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/hungarys-pm-orban-criticises-ukraines-move-stop-ex-president-border-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 12:49:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦伊姆兰·汗律师在定罪上诉失败后仍被禁止投票</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imran-khans-appeal-against-conviction-rejected-by-pakistan-court-lawyer-says-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦前总理伊姆兰·汗的律师表示，在法院驳回了他周四暂缓先前定罪的请求后，他仍然被取消竞选选举的资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/imran-khans-appeal-against-conviction-rejected-by-pakistan-court-lawyer-says-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 12:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>解说：中菲关系还能恶化到什么程度？</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-far-could-china-philippines-relations-worsen-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国和菲律宾都呼吁通过对话解决该战略航道的紧张局势，但两国在捍卫南海领土主张方面加大了言论力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/how-far-could-china-philippines-relations-worsen-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 11:47:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国对芬太尼的压力下，墨西哥发动“假想的禁毒战争”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/under-us-pressure-over-fentanyl-mexico-wages-imaginary-war-drugs-with-raids-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据墨西哥国防部获得的数据，尽管美国施压打击芬太尼贩运，但墨西哥军队似乎每个月只突击搜查少数活跃的毒品实验室，今年查获的毒品实验室中有 95% 是已经闲置的实验室。路透社。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/under-us-pressure-over-fentanyl-mexico-wages-imaginary-war-drugs-with-raids-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 11:08:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利欧尔班：瑞典未能与土耳其就北约申办达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/no-deal-with-turkey-swedish-nato-bid-hungarys-orban-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克托在周四的新闻发布会上表示，匈牙利和土耳其在批准瑞典加入北约问题上没有达成任何协议，因为这将由匈牙利议会决定何时对此进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/no-deal-with-turkey-swedish-nato-bid-hungarys-orban-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 10:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>同性祝福裁决后，教皇谴责僵化的意识形态</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/after-same-sex-blessing-ruling-pope-decries-inflexible-ideologies-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，教皇弗朗西斯警告说，僵化的意识形态立场可能会阻碍教会看清现实并前进，几天前，他发表了允许同性伴侣祝福的声明，遭到保守派的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/after-same-sex-blessing-ruling-pope-decries-inflexible-ideologies-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 10:26:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世卫组织称加沙北部不再有一家正常运转的医院</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/northern-gaza-no-longer-has-functional-hospital-who-says-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界卫生组织周四表示，由于缺乏燃料、人员和物资，加沙北部已经没有一家正常运转的医院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/northern-gaza-no-longer-has-functional-hospital-who-says-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 09:11:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>驱逐俄罗斯军队一年后，乌克兰小镇面临严冬</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukrainian-town-faces-tough-winter-year-after-driving-out-russian-forces-2023-12-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰东部小镇莱曼遭受重创，仅存的少数居民正在为降雪和气温下降的艰难冬季做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukrainian-town-faces-tough-winter-year-after-driving-out-russian-forces-2023-12-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 07:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
